{
  "stem": "12491.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had the shoe makers put new soles on winter shoes, metal nail-like spikes on the shoes, so they would last longer.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I smuggled myself across the river Bug, back into the farm.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I arrived there, sometimes in February, 1940.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "At that point, the Russians were coming into the farm.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were against a Zionist farm existing in their midst.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they said that they going to liquidate it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Since we knew that they-- they liquidated, they would all be sent out further east, deeper into the Russian-- into Russia.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We decided, again, that we have to get my mother and my sister out of-- out of the Crakow.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we already heard, more and more, of the horrible stories that were happening to Jews.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But predominantly, at that time, to males.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They did not bother, so much, women.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They did have to sweep for the streets, and clean toilets, and things like that.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But they-- but nobody was talking about taking somebody's life.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So then-- then, I again smuggled myself into the German part [INAUDIBLE] by Poland.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this became harder each time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because the borders were more guarded.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, that trip was extremely difficult.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was difficult to the point that I spent two days and three nights in bushes on-- on the Russian side of the river, trying to get across while I saw Russian border guards and German border guards on the other side of the river, walking along and had to find a time at which I might be able to safely cross.",
      "word_count": 62
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was with two other people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We found such a time.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this is cutting, making it very short.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This is a long story in its own.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
